examples.en: She guessed my age on her first try.
Have I guessed right or wrong?
He guessed that it would rain today.
She guessed the identity of his lover.
I guessed you not to be here that late.
I had to choose one, and I guessed right.
He is Russian as you might have guessed from his name.
She soon guessed what lay behind his question.
It was colder and windier than I had guessed it would be.
I guessed that you must be related because you look so similar.
He guessed the right number of beans in the jar and won the prize.
We guessed that the plumber had turned the water off at the mains.
I guessed it would cost $100 and it was $110, so I was not far out.
I guessed from his expression that he already knew about the accident.
Who would have guessed that he would fetch up as director of the firm?
As you might have guessed, her parents are not happy about her decision.
